data.description: Renovated Ranch, cozy and beautifully finished. This home has all you need. Unbelievable LOW TAXES. Centrally located close to transportation, railroad, shopping, malls, schools and park. You won''t need anything else other than bringing your furniture and move right in. Features, Brand new boiler. Kitchen with stainless steal appliances and granite tops. Renovated baths. 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths. Full finished basement with 2 additional rooms, recreation room and outside entrance.  Detached garage and a long wide blacktop driveway. Large fenced in yard with sprinklers system. Beautiful landscaping and deck. You will love this home!
